title: #697 - Agostino Zoida
description:
Agostino Zoida, a stand up comedian and the host of the "Home Schooled" podcast, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.

Agostino will be headlining the House of Comedy in Minnesota July 5-7 2019. Get your tickets here: https://bit.ly/2RMWr0Q
